text: Homecoming (2020) was a professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on January 1, 2020 at Daily's Place in Jacksonville, Florida. The event aired as a special episode of Dynamite. It was the first Homecoming event held by AEW. The name of the event was a reference to the company's return to Daily's Place.
